data.description: Upgraded single story pool home in the highly sought after Canyon Lake community! This fully furnished home is ready to be made yours today, and features great curb appeal with California drought tolerant landscaping, and a covered front porch area to enjoy. The interior offers an open concept floor plan with recessed lighting, vaulted ceilings, and tile flooring throughout the main living areas. The living room has a ceiling fan and opens to the dining area and kitchen with granite counters, new stainless steel appliances, bar seating, and a large pantry. The laundry room is just off of the kitchen and there is direct garage access to the attached 2-car garage that is currently transformed into a full size home gym! All 3 bedrooms are generously sized and have ceiling fans. The large primary bedroom offers wood tile flooring, 2 closets, a private slider to the backyard and a private bathroom with walk-in shower and 2 updated vanities. Just outside of the primary suite is a newly built patio cover and deck outfitted with a brand new above ground spa. The secondary bedrooms each have carpet flooring and there is a full-size hall bathroom which also has an updated vanity. This home offer's an entertainer's dream backyard with large concrete area, newly installed turf putting green, and the lower second level has a private swimming pool! Residents of this community also get to enjoy Resort-like amenities including access to a private lake, a golf course, a swimming pool & spa, tennis courts, and so much more! This home is being sold with the golf cart included!!!
